  "description": {
    "zh": "请进，快请进！我给你安排个事情做。这是我的个人事情。我在塔科夫出事儿之前寄了一封信出去。现在我觉得没必要再把事情弄得一团糟了。不是时候。能帮我去邮局看看，那封信还在那里吗？",
    "en": "Come in, come in! I've got something for you to do. It's a personal matter. I sent a letter just before all this mess started in Tarkov. And now I don't think it's worth it to stir it all up. Not the time. Would you look in the post office and see if my letter is still there?"
  },
